===Etymology 2===
Transliteration of various Semitic letters, such as {{translit|en|phn|sc=Phnx|𐤄|tr=h|notext=1}}, {{translit|en|he|sc=Hebr|ה|tr=h|notext=1}}, {{translit|en|syc|sc=Syrc|ܗ|tr=h||hē|notext=1}}, and {{translit|en|sem-srb|sc=Sarb|𐩠|tr=h|notext=1}}.

