==Lakota==

===Particle===
{{head|lkt|particle}}

# ''[[question]]-marking particle used by females in formal speech''
#: {{ux|lkt|Mázaškaŋškaŋ tóna he?|[[what time is it]]?|inline=y}}

====Usage notes====
Informally, both men and women use this question-marking particle. When speaking formally, however, only women use it. In a formal setting, men use {{l|lkt|huwó}}, {{l|lkt|hwo}}, or {{l|lkt|huŋwó}}.

====Synonyms====
* {{l|lkt|huwó}} (used by men)

